# You need installed Node.js

# Also you need installed bower.
# If you don't run: > npm -g install bower

# You need have some experience with Gulp.

# Install node_modules dependencies ( Gupl + gulp plugins ).
> npm install

# Install bower packages. We need this for production.
> bower install

# Run gulp task for build js & css files for production.
> gulp

# For "live-reload" browser use:
> gulp browser-sync

